---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="About Enerama | 14 Years · 27 Projects · 350+ Units"
  description="Enerama Environmental Technologies: full-EPC climate control company with PCT patented Liquid Desiccant platform. 14 years, 27 projects, 350+ units installed across USA, Switzerland & Türkiye."
  keywords="enerama, about enerama, liquid desiccant, climate control, EPC, dragon system, energy efficiency, water recovery"
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative text-white py-20" style="background-color: #0B3D4C;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 text-sm font-medium" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
          Est. 2011 · Türkiye
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
          14 Years. 27 Projects. 350+ Units Deployed.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-200 max-w-3xl">
          Enerama Environmental Technologies is a full-EPC climate control company — we engineer, produce, construct, and commission complete working environments using our patented Liquid Desiccant platform.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
            At Enerama Environmental Technologies, we don't just sell climate systems — we deliver complete working environments that transform how businesses operate.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            Through our full EPC (Engineering, Procurement, and Construction) approach, we take responsibility for every aspect of your project, from initial design through 60-Day Online Support.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Our Vision</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
            To be the global leader in sustainable environmental control, setting new standards for energy efficiency, reliability, and total project accountability.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
            We believe in technology that works for you — backed by our patented platform and unwavering commitment to your success.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Our Journey</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">From first installation to global platform</p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5" style="background-color: #0D7377;"></div>

          <div class="space-y-12">
            <div class="relative flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white z-10" style="background-color: #0D7377;">2011</div>
              <div class="ml-8 flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Founded</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  Enerama established in Istanbul, Türkiye. First Dragon Liquid Desiccant system designed and commissioned.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white z-10" style="background-color: #0D7377;">2014</div>
              <div class="ml-8 flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">International Expansion</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  First projects delivered outside Türkiye. Operations extended to Switzerland and the USA.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white z-10" style="background-color: #0D7377;">2019</div>
              <div class="ml-8 flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Platform Validation</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  10th project commissioned. Dragon platform validated at scale across diverse industrial conditions.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="my-12">
              <img
                src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69c9538c5e6a6b66c71a24ee/69d1177f0cee0ec71a5731d1_20200704_143032.jpg"
                alt="Large-scale Dragon installation at industrial facility"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white z-10" style="background-color: #0D7377;">2023</div>
              <div class="ml-8 flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Solar TES Development</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  R&D begins on Dragon Solar TES — integrating thermal energy storage for fully renewable 24/7 operation.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white z-10" style="background-color: #E07B39;">2026</div>
              <div class="ml-8 flex-1">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">PCT Patent Filed</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  Dragon Solar TES PCT patent filed Q1 2026. 27 projects active across 3 countries. 350+ units installed.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Global Presence — 3 project countries + Baku rep office -->
  <section class="relative py-20" style="background-image: url('https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69c9538c5e6a6b66c71a24ee/69d113bd1d5e0b23aeea512c_IMG-20200709-WA0035.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);"></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Global Presence</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200">
          27 projects delivered across 3 countries, supported by a 4th representation office
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg border-t-4" style="border-color: #1B3A6B;">
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Middle East & Türkiye</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Istanbul, Türkiye</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Headquarters and manufacturing. R&D center and primary operations base.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg border-t-4" style="border-color: #E07B39;">
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: #E07B39;">Americas</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">San Clemente, California, USA</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            North American headquarters. Business development and project delivery.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg border-t-4" style="border-color: #0D7377;">
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: #0D7377;">Europe</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Zürich, Switzerland</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            European operations hub. Project management and client relations for EU-based deployments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Baku — Representation Office (secondary visual weight) -->
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center" style="background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #10B981;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1 text-gray-500">Representation Office</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-1" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Baku, Azerbaijan</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
              Regional business development and partner relations for the Caucasus.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Values -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Our Core Values</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto" style="background-color: #0D7377;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Accountability</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
            We own the entire process — from design to commissioning and beyond. Your success is our responsibility.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto" style="background-color: #0D7377;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Innovation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
            Our PCT patented Liquid Desiccant technology represents breakthrough thinking in environmental control.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto" style="background-color: #0D7377;">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Sustainability</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
            30–70% energy savings and reduced environmental impact through intelligent design and operation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Enerama Difference -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          The Enerama Difference
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1" style="background-color: #E07B39;">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Single Point of Contact</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                No more juggling multiple contractors. We handle design, manufacturing, installation, and commissioning as one cohesive team.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1" style="background-color: #E07B39;">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Proven Technology</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Our PCT patented Liquid Desiccant system delivers measurable results: 30–70% energy savings, 100+ L/h water extraction, and 2–4 year ROI.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1" style="background-color: #E07B39;">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">60-Day Online Support</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We do not disappear after installation. Our team stays engaged for 60 days online, ensuring optimal performance and training your staff.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1" style="background-color: #E07B39;">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">4</span>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Versatile Applications</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                From indoor farming to data centers, pharmaceuticals to greenhouses — we've engineered solutions for 10+ diverse industry sectors.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1" style="background-color: #E07B39;">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">5</span>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Long-Term Partnership</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                Optional Maintenance Service Agreements (MSA) provide ongoing support, ensuring your system continues to perform at peak efficiency.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="py-20" style="background-color: #1B3A6B;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Proven Results</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200">Numbers that demonstrate our commitment to excellence</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #E07B39;">14</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Years of Operation</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600">14 years field-proven</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #E07B39;">27</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Commissioned Projects</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600">USA, Switzerland, Türkiye</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #E07B39;">350+</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Installed Conditioners</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600">2,830 kW total installed power</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Environmental Impact -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          Environmental Impact & Sustainability
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Every Enerama project delivers measurable environmental benefits alongside operational performance. By replacing conventional HVAC with patented Liquid Desiccant technology, each Dragon installation contributes directly to carbon reduction, water conservation, and sustainable energy use.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" style="border-color: #0D7377;">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Carbon Reduction</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            30–70% reduction in climate control energy consumption vs conventional HVAC — directly translating to significant CO₂ emissions reduction per facility.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" style="border-color: #0D7377;">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Clean Energy Integration</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Dragon's low regeneration temperature requirement (50–70°C) makes it compatible with solar thermal energy. Our next-generation Solar TES module — currently in pre-commercial development — is designed to enable fully renewable 24/7 operation when deployed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" style="border-color: #0D7377;">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Reduced Chemical Usage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Liquid desiccant eliminates the need for chemical disinfectants and expensive filter replacements — natural air sterilization with no ongoing chemical costs or waste.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-2 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" style="border-color: #0D7377;">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Natural Air Sterilization</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Concentrated Liquid Desiccant solution naturally eliminates airborne pathogens on contact — bacteria, mold spores, and viruses — without chemicals or UV systems. This makes Dragon particularly valuable in food, agriculture, and health-sensitive environments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Partner With Us</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Experience the Enerama difference — complete accountability, proven technology, and unwavering support.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
        style="background-color: #E07B39;"
      >
        Get Started Today
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
